{"tid":2213750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"摺紙鶴靜坐後協助搬磚 售貨員獲保釋候判 另外兩名被告以簽保守行為方式處理","createTime":"2020-09-22T18:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T19:49:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a9563bf56a6172cf7f24544c03152a1d3929fe83","tid":2213750,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:13:34.000Z","msg":"售貨員去年11月在秀茂坪某商場參與摺紙鶴靜坐活動，及後應邀到附近休憩處，其間見人掘磚後協助搬磚，最終與兩名少年男女一同被警員拘捕。售貨員今在觀塘裁判法院承認刑事毀壞罪，裁判官指當日現場沒有示威，亦沒證據顯示售貨員涉及進一步不法行為；而且案中三人罪責相同，惟另外兩名被告早前已先後獲撤控，改以簽保守行為方式處理。為公平起見，裁判官認為三人的判刑不應有太大落差，故下令先索取感化及社會服務令報告，下月8日始判刑，其間售貨員可保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/2MC2SJYNFBGLTBOGNZYPSJISK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2F2MC2SJYNFBGLTBOGNZYPSJISK4%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I251QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=b03cd5d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2F2MC2SJYNFBGLTBOGNZYPSJISK4%2F&h=033bf430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/2MC2SJYNFBGLTBOGNZYPSJISK4/</a>"},{"pid":"abb4fd9f158866864d40b8468bbe05fc43a5d425","tid":2213750,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:26:49.000Z","msg":"邊個官"},{"pid":"54529a72a37a0f45cae8491da5d4ede654a38028","tid":2213750,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ad43a715255f33fb6bf715ab583661c40716e6","tid":2213750,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54529a72a37a0f45cae8491da5d4ede654a38028","tid":2213750,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:50:56.00